$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.Every guy in town wants to set up an appointment with Doctor Amor. I’m not sure how good she is as a doctor though. The life expectancy in this town ranks pretty low.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.Here’s a tip buddy. If you lay low enough on the examination table you might just catch a peak up Doctor Amor’s skirt.");
As the one year anniversary approaches of Hurricane Evelyn surrounding cities still struggle to overcome the damage.
Luckily Cape Vedra was spared from a direct hit.
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.Actually I wanted to talk to you about my 5friend, Kaley.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.I have a shipment for Dr. Jessica Amor. It’s heart medicine.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeFrEx.You can put it in the supply room. Thank you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeSaEx.I’m sorry for the interruption. I’ve never had to stock so much heart medicine until I moved here to Cape Vedra. The citizens here can be so unhealthy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.Oh.. Well.. It’s my 5friend. She needs some help and I think you can help her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiWoEx^.I’ve been bit by a Cape Vedra viper!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeWoOp.My antidotes are only for spider bites and scorpion stings. I’ve not had to treat a viper bite before.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeWoOp.Where did you run across a venomous snake?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiWoEx^.It was in the cave. They only like dark cool places…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiSaEx^.There was a path in the cave... it went deeper than before. I went too far...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeHaEx.I know the caves! I can help you!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiWoEx^.You can’t 1Hero. You don’t have a license for cave spelunking.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeSaEx.Please relax Michael. We need to slow your heart rate.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeWoEx.Go to the caves 1Hero. Find a viper and bring it to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeWoOp.And whatever you do, don’t get bit.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeWoOp.I can slow down his heart rate to keep him alive. But don’t be long.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.I can do it Jessica! You can count on me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaDe.I need to find a snake in a cave. This sounds dangerous. If only there were a way for me to get a rock bomb like Clare had. I could go much deeper.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Jessica, I have the original love potion to give to you...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.I drank a bit of it. And it’s more powerful than Emily’s formula... So...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeWoEx.You know 1Hero. If you really want to have sex you can just ask.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.This time is a bit different... I wanted to know what it tasted like.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeFlEx.Why don’t you leave the testing to Emily and I.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeFrEx.Come on 1Hero. Let’s get you fixed up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeFrOp.Thank you for dropping off the love potion. I’ll see what information I can find out for Emily.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeWoEx.In the meantime, you shouldn’t be drinking this, or any other love potion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.I get it. And if I do, I know where to come.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeShCl.1Hero! You make it sound like you’re planning to get into trouble.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.What is the reason for the visit?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaWoCl.Hello Miss. I’m not sick or anything. I... I...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeFrEx.It’s okay Kaley. 1Hero told me a little about your problem. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeFrOp.Why don’t the two of you come into the exam room?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaWoCl.I can’t believe her methods! She’s crazy!...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaSaCl.I’m sorry if it was weird for you 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlEx.It was fun as hell for me!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaWoCl.Do you think it’s weird that I was there?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Well... I’m almost used to it now. You’ve seen me do it twice.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaFrOp.It's like old times 1Hero. I really feel you care about me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlDe.Even if sometimes you can be a little annoying.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaHaEx.I’m not annoying! You’re just mad because you can never beat me in anything.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlEx.I’m not as weak as I was when I was a kid Kaley. I’m a grown man now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaFrOp.1Hero... Are you going back to the cave?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.The park ranger is probably there now that Sam reported a dead body.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaFrEx.It’s just... It’s very interesting. I had no idea that there were big caves in Cape Vedra.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.Oh yeah. I’ve found several big cavern rooms. But it’s very dangerous down there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaEx.Kaley. I shouldn’t have said anything. It’s unexplored territory. It’s not safe for you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoEx.I know 1Kaley. But 2Janet would kill me if I got you into trouble...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.Hell, she may kill me anyway if she ever found out I’ve been in those caves.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.You know... 2Janet is very lonely at home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaEx.She’ll be even more lonely when you leave for school.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.Just keep an eye on her. She really enjoys your company Kaley.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KaFrOp.You’re a caring person... You’ve grown up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.I’ve always cared... It’s just... my priorities were different before I left.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.But I like being here in Cape Vedra. It still feels like home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaDe.Speaking of the caves... I wonder if Clare has returned with her goons. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.Once she sees that the rocks have been blasted away, she’ll know it was me who did it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JaFrEx.Hello. 4Hero here has been bitten by a rat. He may need to get a rabies shot.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JaWoOp.1Hero! Have you already been to the doctor for something else?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.Oh uhh.. I fell and bumped my head.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AbFlAg.Bring that booty over here! It begs for a smackin’!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.Albert! You have to stop! You’re going to give Emily’s love potion a bad name!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AbHaAg.Stand back 1Hero! Albert needs to find more ladies for some good old fashioned booty smacks!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.He’s too big to stop. And the love potion has given him unnatural speed and youthful vigor.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoSa.I’m going to need something to take him down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EmWoEx.Quick! These two need to see the doctor right away. Something happened to them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "EmWoEx.10 grams between the two of them!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JeWoOp>.Oh no! We must treat this right away!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "TaWoCl.I feel like I’m going to throw up.");
